reviewText: Fun movies for the whole family! Movies that are made with adults AND kids in mind are difficult to find. These fit that bill perfectly.
Movie was great. Arrived in timely fashion.
Great price and amazing collection to own.

The Road to El Dorado is bright and bouncy and keeps up the energy throughout. I loved the story and the way it was told. Two scoundrels sneak aboard a ship bound for the New Lands and find themselves in their search for gold. Sinbad has an equally energetic re-telling and it s very good. You are captivated by the monsters and adventures he and his crew encounter while searching for proof Sinbad was framed for a crime. Joseph is a religious myth fable that is OK.

My wife is a 6th grade teacher and decided to give the kids a little break after they finished all their hard work on those crazy state tests.  She asked me to order El Dorado and I found this 3 movie collection for the price of 1 movie.  It replaces the old VHS movie we played for years when my own kids were young.  It is a great value and the movies are fun to watch with the young'uns.  Get it if like good clean fun for the kids you'll be pleased.
Fine for me to watch but El Dorado was NOT appropriate for my toddlers or even young children. It is way to sexual for a family movie!
It came to my house and box was open put everything was their so it all good
Kids loved the movies. No problems with the quality.
I bought for eldorado witch was wayyyy better than I remembered. Was surprised to like sinbad as much as I did! Had never seen it before.
Great price for 3 really good memorable movies.
A favorite from years ago. Keeps me laughing the whole way through
